Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:08.060 --> 00:00:11.720
Losing has a cause of concern for both men and women

00:00:11.720 --> 00:00:14.800
bald patches is the most visible sign in men

00:00:14.800 --> 00:00:18.780
with a receding hairline and little or no hair on the head

00:00:18.780 --> 00:00:24.220
heredity factors play a big role especially when it comes to male pattern balding

00:00:24.220 --> 00:00:29.240
in women other factors like hormonal imbalance leads to thinning of hair

00:00:29.240 --> 00:00:34.400
however what is common to both men and women when it comes to losing hair is stress

00:00:34.660 --> 00:00:40.040
other causes include underlying chronic in ailments like anaemia or typhoid etc

00:00:40.040 --> 00:00:46.220
vitamin B6 and folic acid deficiency or an unclean scalp with clogged follicles

00:00:46.220 --> 00:00:51.820
try using these simple ingredients available in your kitchen to help prevent hair loss

00:00:56.940 --> 00:01:00.340
in a pan boil a cup of mustard oil

00:01:00.340 --> 00:01:06.060
to the boiling oil add 4 tablespoons of mehendi or henna leaves

00:01:06.060 --> 00:01:09.380
once this cools strain this oil into a bowl

00:01:09.390 --> 00:01:13.500
store this in a clean bottle and massage the oil gently on your scalp

00:01:18.860 --> 00:01:23.400
take an egg yolk and add 1 teaspoon of
honey

00:01:23.400 --> 00:01:27.000
mix this well and apply it to bald patches

00:01:27.000 --> 00:01:30.020
leave it on for about half an hour and then wash it off

00:01:30.090 --> 00:01:32.630
alternatively you can take an egg yolk

00:01:32.630 --> 00:01:35.950
and beat it until it becomes smooth and creamy

00:01:35.950 --> 00:01:40.510
now apply this on your scalp leave it
for half &amp; hour and wash it off

00:01:40.510 --> 00:01:44.030
to avoid a hair fall do not comb your hair when it is wet

00:01:44.030 --> 00:01:49.000
oil your hair once or twice a week and remember to massage your scalp really well

00:01:49.000 --> 00:01:51.140
as this stimulates hair growth

00:01:51.150 --> 00:01:54.930
follow these remedies and enjoy a head full of healthy hair

